room_title: Escape room "Death Row" by Break Free Escape Room in Houston
review: My family had a blast doing both rooms on New Years Eve. We were able to defeat the Ring. Death Row killed us though. Lots of fun and interesting puzzles.

room_title: Escape room "Death Row" by Break Free Escape Room in Houston
review: We had an awesome time! First time escapers for most of us and Death Row almost got us! Super easy to book and staff was amazing! We will be back for sure!

room_title: Escape room "Death Row" by Break Free Escape Room in Houston
review: This was an amazing experience. It was a great date night! We tried the Death Row and it was great! Will definitely come back. There was a great vibe to this place and I hope it thrives!
